OL,6,GA textbook example is unfolding of a
OL,7,Gself-inflicted PR problem at the BBC.
OL,9,FNews of a change in format for Blue
OL,10,FPeter became public knowledge through
OL,11,Fa social media post by much-loved
OL,12,Fformer presenter Simon Thomas, now a
OL,13,Frespected sports broadcaster.
OL,15,FBP will no longer be broadcast live on
OL,16,Fa linear channel and will appear first
OL,17,Fon the iPlayer.
OL,19,FSimon made a point of stressing that
OL,20,FBP is not finishing.
