OL,6,FThe exact change in format is not
OL,7,Fclear at the time of writing.
OL,9,FWill BP simply be pre-recorded or go
OL,10,Fout live on the iPlayer? Or will the
OL,11,Fshow's character change?
OL,13,FBut a few things are clear.
OL,15,
