OL,6,F"Blue Peter won't just be available to
OL,7,Fview online and will remain on the
OL,8,FCBBC and BBC Two linear channels, as
OL,9,Fwell as BBC iPlayer and sign zone. The
OL,10,Fprogramme has been a mix of live and
OL,11,Fpre-recorded shows for decades and has
OL,12,Ftransitioned to a pre-record model as
OL,13,Fviewing habits change."Blue Peter
OL,14,Fcontinues to be loved by generations
OL,15,Facross the UK. As we continue to
OL,16,Fnavigate a challenging market and
OL,17,Fyoung audience viewing habits evolve,
OL,18,Fit is necessary to make some changes
OL,19,Fto ensure that BBC Studios Kids &
OL,20,FFamily Productions delivers a dynamic,
OL,21,Fdigital-first brand that will future-
OL,22,Fproof the show and sustain its legacy
OL,23,Ffor years to come."
